  <p>The main focus on 12th Five year plan as follows: <br>Learning Outcomes and Continuous Comprehensive Evaluation (CCE) <br>
 Ensuring Residual Access and Equity – Regional, Social & Gender <br>
 Pre-Primary Education for School Preparedness<br>
